fields.author: Diego Marin
fields.comment: Thanks to the possibility of being able to promote my destinations outside Colombia, I have been able to contact more potential allies to work internationally.
fields.comment_es: Gracias a la posibilidad de poder promocionar mis destinos fuera de Colombia he podido contactar más aliados potenciales para trabajar a nivel internacional.
fields.comment_en: Thanks to the possibility of being able to promote my destinations outside Colombia, I have been able to contact more potential allies to work internationally.
fields.comment_de: Dank der Möglichkeit, meine Ziele außerhalb Kolumbiens zu bewerben, konnte ich mehr potenzielle Verbündete kontaktieren, um international zu arbeiten.

fields.author: Hotel Casa Hotel
fields.comment: Travel&Solutions has given us the opportunity to show our hotel, the good gastronomy we offer and the service we have.
fields.comment_es: Travel&Solutions nos ha brindado la oportunidad de poder mostrar nuestro hotel, la buena gastronomía qué brindamos y el servicio que tenemos.
fields.comment_en: Travel&Solutions has given us the opportunity to show our hotel, the good gastronomy we offer and the service we have.
fields.comment_de: Travel&Solutions hat uns die Möglichkeit gegeben, unser Hotel, die gute Gastronomie, die wir anbieten, und unseren Service zu zeigen.

fields.author: Anónimo
fields.comment: We always knew that the more people who visited our beaches, the more customers would visit us and get to know this paradise.
fields.comment_es: Siempre supimos que mientras más personas conocieran nuestras playas, mas serian los clientes que nos visitarían y conocerían este paraíso.
fields.comment_en: We always knew that the more people who visited our beaches, the more customers would visit us and get to know this paradise.
fields.comment_de: Wir wussten immer, dass je mehr Menschen unsere Strände besuchten, desto mehr Kunden würden uns besuchen und dieses Paradies kennenlernen.
